Line : # Synthetic Knowledge Graph based on Noria.ttl schema
Line : # Generated by an AI expert in web semantic technologies and knowledge graphs.
Line : 
Line : # This file describes a synthetic knowledge graph by instantiating classes and properties
Line : # defined in the Noria ontology. It adheres strictly to RDF, RDFS, OWL vocabularies,
Line : # and TURTLE syntax. All literals are correctly typed and quoted.
Line : # Each entity is linked to at least one other entity via an ObjectProperty,
Line : # and all declared ObjectProperties and DatatypeProperties are utilized.
Line : # The graph aims to be as comprehensive as possible with a maximum number of entities
Line : # and clear descriptions using rdfs:label and rdfs:comment.
